			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				If you are having a problem with arrows going from your quiver to the ammo slot, remember that you need at LEAST 1 arrow in the ammo slot.  That arrow will remain there until the last of it's kind is used up.  At this time you will then have to place a new arrow into your ammo slot.<BR>
<BR>
I to agree that the Quiver should go in the ammo slot... after reading these messages I'm going to go and sell my quiver for another backpack.
